Package: text
Type: Package
Title: Analyses of Text using Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Author: Oscar Kjell & Andrew Schwartz
Maintainer: The package maintainer <oscar.kjell@psy.lu.se>
Description: Transforms text variables to word embeddings; where the word embeddings are used to statistically test the mean difference between set of texts, compute semantic similarity scores between texts, predict numerical variables etc.   
